7 An Act relating to schools; amending Section 1,
Chapter 289, O.S.L. 2023, as last amended by Section
8 2, Chapter 480, O.S.L. 2025 (70 O.S. Supp. 2025,
Section 18-114.15), which relates to the minimum
9 salary schedule for certified personnel; modifying
salary schedule amounts beginning in certain school
10 year; updating statutory language; providing an
effective date; and declaring an emergency.
