14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY Section 1, Chapter 289, O.S.L.
16 2023, as last amended by Section 2, Chapter 480, O.S.L. 2025 (70
17 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 18-114.15), is amended to read as follows:
